  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/5167ddd75765b0fbbb19022005753b6d.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/5167ddd75765b0fbbb19022005753b6d.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve your way out of a meticulously crafted diorama in this unique escape room experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/6941e3111f9efa00123bac88056e9b1b.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/6941e3111f9efa00123bac88056e9b1b.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/f093b7e60e23ded8272039807ef3fd01.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/f093b7e60e23ded8272039807ef3fd01.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate the glass box with intuitive click-and-drag controls, examine objects up close, and gather essential items to overcome challenging puzzles. Your objective: find the key and break free!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/36b20851550ae8ce2c1634054f5b3659.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/36b20851550ae8ce2c1634054f5b3659.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/be4a32b7576de69b883ee642f2d086a7.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/be4a32b7576de69b883ee642f2d086a7.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A serene, concentration-inducing soundtrack accompanies your exploration, creating the perfect environment to solve puzzles and uncover the secrets within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/91c779d026477858bdbf360fcc6e2854.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/91c779d026477858bdbf360fcc6e2854.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/dc3f1e5892ba5509fe96b4f7ed170c6e.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/dc3f1e5892ba5509fe96b4f7ed170c6e.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you get stuck while trying to solve a riddle, click the bulb button to get a hint that will help you solve the puzzle you're stuck on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1751521589\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3619950/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1751521589 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p>",
